text: Carrie Lewis DelRosso (born September 10, 1975) is an American politician and businesswoman. She is a member of the Pennsylvania House of Representatives from the 33rd district since 2021. She is the Republican nominee for Lieutenant Governor of Pennsylvania in the 2022 election. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:State legislators of the United States Category:Politicians from Scranton, Pennsylvania Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:Businesspeople from Pennsylvania
